<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>يَفِرُّ يهرب.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>[سورة عبس <span class="c2">(٨٠)</span> : الآيات ٣٥ الى ٤٢]<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَأُمِّهِ وَأَبِيهِ <span class="c2">(٣٥)</span> وَصاحِبَتِهِ وَبَنِيهِ <span class="c2">(٣٦)</span> لِكُلِّ امْرِئٍ مِنْهُمْ يَوْمَئِذٍ شَأْنٌ يُغْنِيهِ <span class="c2">(٣٧)</span> وُجُوهٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ مُسْفِرَةٌ <span class="c2">(٣٨)</span> ضاحِكَةٌ مُسْتَبْشِرَةٌ <span class="c2">(٣٩)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَوُجُوهٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ عَلَيْها غَبَرَةٌ <span class="c2">(٤٠)</span> تَرْهَقُها قَتَرَةٌ <span class="c2">(٤١)</span> أُولئِكَ هُمُ الْكَفَرَةُ الْفَجَرَةُ <span class="c2">(٤٢)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٣٥-<span class="c5"> وَأُمِّهِ وَأَبِيهِ:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وهما أولى الناس بالوفاء لهما.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٣٦-<span class="c5"> وَصاحِبَتِهِ وَبَنِيهِ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَصاحِبَتِهِ وزوجته.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٣٧-<span class="c5"> لِكُلِّ امْرِئٍ مِنْهُمْ يَوْمَئِذٍ شَأْنٌ يُغْنِيهِ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>مِنْهُمْ من هؤلاء.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>يَوْمَئِذٍ فى هذا اليوم.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>شَأْنٌ يُغْنِيهِ شأن يشغله.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٣٨-<span class="c5"> وُجُوهٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ مُسْفِرَةٌ:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>مُسْفِرَةٌ مضيئة.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>٣٩-<span class="c5"> ضاحِكَةٌ مُسْتَبْشِرَةٌ:</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>ضاحِكَةٌ مشرقة.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>مُسْتَبْشِرَةٌ مسرورة بنعيم الله.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>٤٠-<span class="c5"> وَوُجُوهٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ عَلَيْها غَبَرَةٌ:</span><a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>غَبَرَةٌ غبار وكدرة.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>٤١-<span class="c5"> تَرْهَقُها قَتَرَةٌ:</span><a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>تَرْهَقُها تغشاها.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>قَتَرَةٌ ظلمة وسواد.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>٤٢-<span class="c5"> أُولئِكَ هُمُ الْكَفَرَةُ الْفَجَرَةُ:</span><a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>الْكَفَرَةُ الْفَجَرَةُ الذين لا يبالون ما ارتكبوا من المعاصي.<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>